name: Where West Meets East
description: Collaboration project between Lucius Felimus (architecture & environment design) and Daney C. (vehicle design and branding). Procedural cyberpunk city generated using Voronoi displacement textures on different meshes of geometry with added holograms, traffic, and atmospheric effects. Rendered in Blender Eevee. Featured OBJKT: #11468 '0037' by @_0ND1.
